民政部回应“武汉小区造假”事件。
Ministry of Civil Affairs responds to "Wuhan district counterfeiting" incident.
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻 综合报道国务院联防联控机制3月9日举行新闻发布会。
The surging news reported a press conference on March 9 by the State Council's Joint Prevention and Control Mechanism.
针对武汉市青山区翠园社区开元公馆小区“假的做法”，民政部基层政权建设和社区治理司司长陈越良表示，这严重伤害了组织“肌体”、严重损害了党和政府的形象，要不得，应坚决纠正。
According to Chen Yuliang, director of the grass-roots regime-building and community governance department of the Ministry of Civil Affairs, this has seriously harmed the organization's "body" and seriously damaged the image of the Party and the government.
此前报道3月5日上午，中央指导组在武汉市青山区翠园社区开元公馆小区考察时，有居民从家里的窗户大喊：“假的，假的”，反映社区物业假装让志愿者送菜送肉给业主、实际工作不到位的情况，引起全社会广泛关注。
As previously reported, on the morning of March 5, the Central Steering Group visited the neighborhood of Kaiyuan Mansion in Qingshan District, Wuhan City. Some residents shouted "fake and fake" from the windows of the house, reflecting the fact that the community property pretended to let volunteers deliver meat to the owners and the actual work was not in place.
此前报道《武汉居民大喊“假的”，中央指导组动了真格》，戳图可查看详情澎湃评论这是一次非常有意义的民意表达与对民意的回应。
Wuhan residents shouted "fake," the Central Steering Group moved the real case, the stamp diagram can see the details of the roar comment This is a very meaningful expression of public opinion and public response.
中央指导组去一线调查，就是为了了解真实情况，解决真实问题。
The Central Steering Group went to the frontline investigation to find out the real situation and solve the real problems.
弄虚作假既是糊弄市民，又是对指导组工作的干扰，幸好有那声发自本能的嘹亮呼喊，让一切都穿帮了。
False fraud is not only to fool the public, but also to the work of the steering group of interference, fortunately from the sound of a clear and instinctive cry, let everything through to help.
疫情是一面镜子，把所有人、所有事照得清清楚楚，真的假不了，假的真不了。
The epidemic is a mirror, all the people, all the things clearly, true can't be false, not true.
从疫情开始到现在，从武汉、湖北到全国，每个环节每个岗位做得如何，公众心中一直有数。
From the beginning of the epidemic to the present, from Wuhan, Hubei to the whole country, every link of how well each post, the public mind has been known.
对于那些牺牲奉献者，人们从来不吝于褒奖，对于那些作假添乱者，人们则会径直戳穿、大张挞伐。
For those who sacrifice devotees, people never hesitate to praise, but for those who make mistakes, people take some apparent telltale signs.
归根结底，只需要回到“实事求是”这四个大字上来。
In the final analysis, it is only a matter of returning to the four big words "seeking truth from facts."
（综合自澎湃新闻记者 王俊、首席评论员 西坡、中国新闻网等）戳这里进入“全国新型冠状病毒感染病例实时地图”↓↓↓本期编辑周玉华推荐阅读。
(Wee Chow, PhD, editor of this PhD) have been singled out for a "real-time map of new cases of coronavirus infection across the country."
